snippet.title: Dhurandhar First Look | Ranveer Singh | Aditya Dhar | In Cinemas 5th December 2025
snippet.description:
Uncover the story of unknown men and their unstoppable fight! 

#Dhurandhar – First look out now.
In Cinemas 5th December 2025.

Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film

Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

snippet.title: Namit Malhotra's Ramayana: The Introduction | Nitesh Tiwari | Ranbir, Yash, Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
snippet.description:
An outcome through a collaboration of some of the world’s best to ensure that Ramayana is presented with the greatest amount of Reverence and Respect. 

Welcome to the Beginning. 

Let’s celebrate the IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana. 

Our Truth. Our History.

Directed by Nitesh Tiwari, Produced by Namit Malhotra’s Prime Focus Studios and 8-time Oscar winning VFX studio DNEG in association with Yash’s Monster Mind Creations; Ramayana is being filmed for IMAX and will release worldwide: Part 1 on Diwali 2026 and Part 2 on Diwali 2027.

Namit Malhotra’s Ramayana

Starring:
Ranbir Kapoor as Rama
Yash as Ravana
Sai Pallavi as Sita
Ravie Dubey as Lakshman
Sunny Deol as Hanuman

Co-Produced by Yash
Written by Shridhar Raghavan
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari

Music by Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
Lyrics by Kumar Vishwas

VFX by DNEG (8-time Academy Award winners)

Filmed for IMAX

Presented by Prime Focus Studios in association with Monster Mind Creations

Audio on Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd (C) 2025

snippet.title: Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu – Konark Express | Episode 03 🤣 #MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu – Konark Express | Episode 03 🤣 #mcm 
Cross paths. Date local -  https://gethap.pn/zgB7

Middle class Monkeys : https://youtube.com/@middleclassmonkeys_filmymoji?si=7OmpZGDGUiF7UbCM

🚆 FilmyMoji Presents: Middle Class Madhu – Konark Express Episode!
Join Madhu, his parents, friends, and our beloved 1A Master as they board the Konark Express for a laugh-out-loud journey to Puri Jagannath! Packed with middle-class comedy, emotional bonding, and unexpected twists on the train, this episode is a rollercoaster on rails! 🛤️😄

👨‍👩‍👦‍👦 Get ready for:

Quirky antics inside the train 🧳

1A Master’s hilarious punchlines 📚

Mahesh’s dad’s iPhone drama 📱

Unexpected middle-class moments you’ll relate to!

🛕 This journey to Puri Yatra sets the tone for a spiritual and comic adventure like never before. Don’t miss this laugh-packed ride!

👍 Like | 💬 Comment | 🔁 Share | 🔔 Subscribe for more MCM madness!

snippet.title: Blessed With Baby Boy Allhamdullilah👶🏻❤️ | Adnaan 07
snippet.description:
Today, my life changed forever.
I became a father and Alhamdulillah, it’s a baby boy.

The moment I heard his first cry, something inside me shifted. A love I never knew existed was born. It’s hard to put into words what it feels like, but I tried capturing every moment, every emotion, and every heartbeat.

This video holds one of the most precious memories of my life. The arrival of my son. The nervousness, the joy, the tears, and the silent prayers.

Thank you for being a part of this journey. Your love and duas mean more than words can ever say.

This is the beginning of something truly beautiful. Do remember us in your prayers.✨

#FathersLove #BabyBoy #Adnaan07 #AdnaanShaikh

snippet.title: Raj Thackeray Speech Funny Punch : राज ठाकरेंच्या पंचवर Supriya Sule, Rashmi Thackeray खळखळून हसल्या
snippet.description:
The Thackeray brothers' victory rally is being held today at the NSCI Dome in Worli. Preparations are in full swing for this rally. It has been reported that only the Thackeray brothers will be on the stage at the victory rally. Their victory rally is being considered important in the backdrop of the municipal elections. The whole of Maharashtra was wondering whether the two Thackeray brothers will come together and form an alliance. Maharashtra is likely to get its answer today. The entire organization is also curious about whether the announcement of the alliance regarding the Thackeray brothers, which is in the minds of the people, will be made today or not. 

वरळीतील NSCI डोममध्ये आज ठाकरे बंधूंचा विजयी मेळावा होत आहे. या मेळाव्याची जय्यत तयारी सुरू आहे. विजयी मेळाव्याला मंचावर फक्त ठाकरे बंधू असणार अशी माहिती मिळाली आहे. महानगरपालिका निवडणुकीच्या पार्श्वभूमीवर त्यांचा हा विजयी मेळावा महत्त्वाचा मानला जात आहे. दोन्ही ठाकरे बंधू एकत्र येत युती करणार का असा प्रश्न संपूर्ण महाराष्ट्राला पडला होता. त्याचं उत्तर आज महाराष्ट्राला मिळण्याची शक्यता आहे. जनतेच्या मनातील ठाकरे बंधूंबद्दल असलेली युतीची घोषणा आज होणार की नाही याची देखील उत्सुकता संपूर्ण म आयोजन करण्यात आलं आहे.

snippet.title: Headlights - Udta Jaaye @alok (ft. @KRSNAOfficial & @RashmeetKaur ) | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When DJ Alok touched down in India, we knew we had to cook up a banger 💥
With your favorites @KRSNAOfficial and @RashmeetKaur on the track...we turned the heat all the way up 🔥🎶

SONG LYRICS:

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
O-Ohhh junoon har saans mein,
O-Ohhh hatheli par hai jaan,
O-Ohhh tum hi rakho zameen,
O-Ohhh mera hai aasmaan.

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

Dekho aaj bhi main ladoon jaise kuchh nahi hai khone ko,
Kone kone mein jaane log, ab poochhe na kaun hai woh.
Itne sapne dekhe toh milta nahi hai sona ko,
Iss game mein top brass, ye peetal bolenge sona ko.
Bole kaam kar, maine kare kaam fir,
Hota na pareshan, meri lage jaan fir,
Subah chale shaam, chale sar-e-aam fir,
Jab kalam se chale chaal, bane kalamkaar fir.


O-Ohhh har pal hai aakhri, O-Ohhh hai kal ki kya khabar,
O-Ohhh jeena hai aaj mein, O-Ohhh haan hoon main befikr.
Ho-Ooo hai aag seene mein, Ho-Toh maza hai jeene mein,
O-Aaa har pal se zindagi, Oo-Aa jee bhar ke jee lenge.

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

Kari hai raat kaali,
Dekhe maine bhi khwaab,
Haan mushkil dekhe maine din,
Dekhe maine bhi raat.
Iss level se na sehmati hai,
Mujhse mehnati kaun?
I got the skill to make
A kill N wipe an enemy squad.
I say – Booyah!
Jaake la tu crew-ya,
Kaun hai tu yaar?
Coz I never knew-ya.
Coz I never knew-ya.
I’m making moves-ya,
Ikattha karoon loot-ya,
Phir bhi tu lage noob,
Coz I’m shootin through-ya.
I’m singing…

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

アブ・トゥ・ユー・ウダ・ジャイエ、ディル・メラ・ウダ・ジャイエ、
ジョー・チャヘ・ウォパ・ジャアイ、アワラ・ウダ・ジャアイ。

ああ、ジュヌーン・ハル・サーンス・メイン、
ああ、ハテリ・パー・ハイ・ジャーン、
ああ、こんにちは、ラコー・ザミーン、

そうだ、私の心は飛んでいる、どこへ行くべきかなんて聞かないで。

いいか、今日も私は愚か者で、失うものは何もない。
人々はあちこちと行ってしまう、さあ、それが誰なのか聞いてみろ。
こんなにたくさんの夢を見た後でも、ソナはこのゲームで上層部を得ることはできない、これらの花びらがソナを呼ぶだろう。

働かせてくれ、そうすれば私は働く。
私は心配しない、また気分が良くなるだろう。
朝晩歩かせてくれ、また真っ向から歩かせてくれ。
ペンが動けば、私はまた作家になるだろう。
ああ、一瞬一瞬が最後、ああ、明日のニュースはどうなるのだろう、

それは暗い夜だった、

私は夢も見た、

そうだ、昼間の困難も見た、

夜も見た。

私にはこんな忍耐力はない、

私より勤勉な人がいるだろうか？

私には、敵部隊を倒したり全滅させるスキルがある。

ブーヤー！

仲間の所へ行け、

お前は誰だ？

だって、お前のことなんて知らなかったんだから。

だって、お前のことなんて知らなかったんだから。

俺は動いている、
一緒に略奪しよう、
でも、お前はまだ初心者に見える、
だって、俺は撃ち抜いているんだから。
俺は歌っている…

今、俺の心は飛んでいる、俺の心は飛んでいる、

snippet.title: ഈ പീറപ്പെണ്ണാണോ എന്റെ അമ്മ എന്ന് സത്യൻ സാർ ചോദിച്ചു | Sathyan | Adoor Bhavani old interview
snippet.description:
ഈ പീറപ്പെണ്ണാണോ എന്റെ അമ്മ എന്ന് സത്യൻ സാർ ചോദിച്ചു | Sathyan | Adoor Bhavani | #kairalitv #kairalinews 
Adoor Bhavani (1927 – 25 October 2009) was an Indian actress in Malayalam cinema, best known for her appearance in the National Award-winning film Chemmeen (1965), directed by Ramu Kariat. She had acted in about 450 films, including Mudiyanaya Puthran, Thulabharam, Kallichellamma, and Anubhavangal Paalichakal. Her last film was K. Madhu-directed Sethurama Iyer CBI. She was also a stage actress and was associated with popular theatre group KPAC.

Bhavani was born in Adoor in Travancore.Her sister, Adoor Pankajam, was also a Malayalam film actress. Adoor Bhavani died on 25 October 2009.

snippet.title: Aa Samiya - Hansraj Raghuwanshi | Himachali Song | Official Video | Sawan Special Bhole Baba Song
snippet.description:
Aa Samiya - Hansraj Raghuwanshi | Himachali Song | Official Video | Sawan Special Bhole Baba Song 
#aasamiya #hansrajraghuwanshi #shivbhajan #himachalisong
__________
"Aa Samiya"  | शिव  नुआला:  
यह कोई साधारण गीत नहीं, बल्कि भगवान शिव को समर्पित एक लोक गायन परंपरा का हिस्सा है, जो हिमाचल प्रदेश के गद्दी समुदाय से जुड़ी है।

जब किसी की मनोकामना पूरी होती है, जब घर में कोई विशेष खुशी या उत्सव होता है, तब गद्दी लोग अपने आराध्य भगवान शिव को धन्यवाद देने हेतु, नुआला लोक उत्सव का आयोजन करते हैं।

यह उत्सव पूरी रात चलता है, जिसमें भगवान शिव की स्तुति, लोक भजन, और भक्ति की गूंज सुनाई देती है।
इसमें भगवान शिव से प्रार्थना की जाती है —
"भूखे को अन्न, प्यासे को पानी, अंधे को आंखें दो... और इस दुनिया का कल्याण कीजिए।"

अगर आपने आज तक कोई नुआला नहीं सुना,
तो "Aa Samiya" से शुरुआत करें।
 यह गीत नहीं, भगवान शिव से जुड़ने का मार्ग।

जब किसी की मनोकामना पूरी होती है, जब घर में कोई विशेष खुशी या उत्सव होता है, तब गद्दी लोग अपने आराध्य भगवान शिव को धन्यवाद देने हेतु, नुआला लोक उत्सव का आयोजन करते हैं।

यह उत्सव पूरी रात चलता है, जिसमें भगवान शिव की स्तुति, लोक भजन, और भक्ति की गूंज सुनाई देती है।
इसमें भगवान शिव से प्रार्थना की जाती है —
"भूखे को अन्न, प्यासे को पानी, अंधे को आंखें दो... और इस दुनिया का कल्याण कीजिए।"

अगर आपने आज तक कोई नुआला नहीं सुना,
तो "Aa Samiya" से शुरुआत करें।
 यह गीत नहीं, भगवान शिव से जुड़ने का मार्ग।

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: KGF Chapter 1 - The Most Unpredictable Twist Scene| Yash | Prashanth Neel | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
KGF Chapter 1 wasn't just about action and swag—it was layered with twists that left everyone stunned. But one moment changed everything. In this video, we break down the most unpredictable scene that flipped the story and revealed Rocky's true motives.

Written & Directed by: Prashanth Neel 
Starring: Yash, Srinidhi Shetty, Ayyapa, B Suresh, Srinivas Murthy, Archana Jois, Roopa Rayappa, Master Anmol, Ananth Nag, Malavika, Achut Kumar, Naga Bharana, Dinesh Mangalur, Harish roi, Ninasam Ashwath, introducing Avinash, Ram, Lucky, Vinay
Produced by: Vijay Kiragandur 
Executive Producer: Karthik, K.V Rama Rao 
Director of Photography : Bhuvan Gowda 
Music, Background, Sound design by : Ravi Basrur

Premalo.. Thappu ledhu premalo.. || 2 ||

Naatho raa chupisthaa aa saradhaa
Nelanthaa chuttese veelundhaa
Emundhi premisthe saripodhaa
Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le
Dhaani ooru manamu le
Ye manasuni yemadagaku ye rujuvini.. Oh.. Anthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu
Unnaayaa bandhinche dhaaraalu
Oohallo untunte praanaalu
Are ningi loni chukkale
Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..

snippet.description:
Ramayana The Introduction Teaser Review By Deeksha Sharma. Namit Malhotra's Ramayana Directed by Nitesh Tiwari Presents Ranbir Kapoor in The IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana- Full of History Detailing, Top Quality Special Effects by DNEG & Powerful yet Unique Background Music Created by Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman Ramayana Promises the Biggest Cinema Adventure ever produced in Indian Film Industry. Starring Ranbir Kapoor as Rama, Yash as Ravana, Sai Pallavi as Sita, Ravie Dubey as Lakshman & Sunny Deol as Hanuman - Ramayana Part 1 is set for Diwali 2026 release date. Ramayana The Introduction Teaser Trailer Review Reaction & full Movie Expectations would be shared in this Video. snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
#vetriduraisamy #saidaiduraisamy #pasumaivikatan #redsandal 

சென்னை மாநகராட்சியின் முன்னாள் மேயரும் அதிமுக மூத்த உறுப்பினருமான சைதை துரைசாமி விவசாயத்திலும் ஆர்வம் கொண்டவர். திருவள்ளூர் மாவட்டம் திருத்தணியில் 25 ஆண்டுகளுக்கு முன்பே 60க்கும் மேற்பட்ட ஏக்கரில் நிலம் வாங்கி அங்கே செம்மரங்களை வளர்த்து வருகிறார். அங்கே நாட்டு மாடுகள், நாய்கள், கோழிகள் மட்டுமல்லாது மறைந்த அவர் மகன் வெற்றி துரைசாமி வளர்த்து வந்த காங்கேயம் காளைகளையும் பராமரித்து வருகிறார். இந்த வீடியோவில் அதுகுறித்து பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறார்.....

snippet.title: Chhodh Ke Na Jaa Ooh Piya (Lyrical Video) | Alka Yagnik | Sunny Deol, Tabu | Maa Tujhhe Salaam
snippet.description:
"Chhodh Ke Na Jaa Ooh Piya" is a soulful and emotional track from the movie Maa Tujhhe Salaam (2002), beautifully sung by Alka Yagnik. The song expresses a deep sense of love, longing, and heartache, as the singer pleads with her lover not to leave. With its heartfelt lyrics and Alka Yagnik’s powerful voice, this song stands out as one of the most poignant and memorable moments in the film.

Danish Taimoor breathes life into Sher Zaman, a man raised with command in his veins—fierce, proud, and built to lead.
Sarah Khan shines as Fajar, a gentle heart swept into the storm of a family feud, trying to hold on to love and light in a world clouded by old grudges.

Their paths were never meant to cross. But love… had other plans.

Sher is a gripping Pakistani drama packed with raw emotions, intense rivalries, and deep-rooted traditions.

Parwarish Episode 25 | Digitally Presented by Surf Excel , Vince Care, Mothercare &  VGOTEL | Aina Asif | Samar Jafri | Reham Rafiq | 1st JULY 2025 | ARY Digital Drama 

PARWARISH – The most-watched Pakistani drama of the season, Parwarish is a gripping tale of generational conflict, where love becomes control and independence feels like rebellion. As parents hold tight to cultural traditions and children chase dreams of freedom, misunderstandings shake the very foundation of the family. It’s a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his father’s disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the drama’s central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctor—a path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in today’s society.

Cast:
Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir
Aina Asif as Maya
Naumaan Ijaz as Jahangir

Nooray Zeeshan as Aania

Arshad Mehmood  as Dada
Saman Ansari
Abul Hasan & others.

Writer: Kiran Siddiqui
Directed by: Meesam Naqvi

snippet.title: Gear Wali Cycle | Standup Comedy Special by Rajat Chauhan (61st video)
snippet.description:
Join Rajat Chauhan on a laugh-out-loud journey through his Delhi childhood! Growing up in DDA flats, Rajat shares hilarious stories of middle-class life, quirky neighbors, and the unique culture that shaped him. Relive the magic of one of Bollywood’s most iconic romantic duets, “Mukh Pe Jo Chhidka Pani”, featuring the melodious voices of Kishore Kumar and Lata Mangeshkar. This heartwarming song from the classic film Dharam Karam (1975) is beautifully brought to life with the stunning on-screen chemistry of Rekha and Randhir Kapoor.

snippet.title: Charity or Showbiz? | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
In this short video, we reflect on a growing concern within our churches,  are we truly giving from the heart, or are we more concerned about our name being announced in public? Too often, people give generously to the church just to gain recognition, while neglecting genuine needs like community development or council initiatives that benefit everyone.

Let’s pause and ask ourselves: Is our giving rooted in love, faith, and responsibility — or is it driven by pride and empty tradition? True giving is quiet, sincere, and purposeful.

snippet.title: Pregnancy Reveal to My Siblings! 😍| You Won’t Believe Their Reaction 😭❤️| Gowti Sowbi
snippet.description:
This is one of the most emotional moments of my life… 🥹
I surprised my siblings with the big news – I’m pregnant! 🍼
My younger brother, who’s usually not expressive, gave a reaction I’ll never forget. His eyes filled with tears… and my heart just melted 😭❤️
My akka and mama were so happy and full of love.

Watch this unforgettable pregnancy reveal and the pure reactions from my siblings. Thank you all for being part of this beautiful journey!

snippet.description:

Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai: 💔😱Armaan से मिले धोखे के बाद Abhira ने थामा Anshuman का हाथ #sbs
snippet.description:
#YeRishtaKyaKehelataHai #YRKKH #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #abhira #armaan 

*Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai* is a long-running Indian television drama that explores family relationships, love, and societal dynamics through its evolving storylines. The show, which began with Akshara and Naitik's journey, has progressed through generations, maintaining its core theme of familial bonds. In the current track, the focus has shifted to a new generation, highlighting the lives of Abhira (the union of Abhimanyu and Akshara's legacy), Armaan, and Ruhi. These characters navigate their relationships, ambitions, and the challenges of their lineage while upholding the values of the Goenka and Birla families. The blend of drama, emotions, and cultural nuances continues to resonate with viewers, ensuring its enduring popularity.

Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. Presenting you the latest updates and daily dose of entertainment in the form of star cast interviews, gossips, updates of reality shows, behind the scenes, twist in serials. Join the non stop entertainment with Saas Bahu aur Saazish for all the cool and juicy news.

localized.description:
#YeRishtaKyaKehelataHai #YRKKH #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #abhira #armaan 

*Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai* is a long-running Indian television drama that explores family relationships, love, and societal dynamics through its evolving storylines. The show, which began with Akshara and Naitik's journey, has progressed through generations, maintaining its core theme of familial bonds. In the current track, the focus has shifted to a new generation, highlighting the lives of Abhira (the union of Abhimanyu and Akshara's legacy), Armaan, and Ruhi. These characters navigate their relationships, ambitions, and the challenges of their lineage while upholding the values of the Goenka and Birla families. The blend of drama, emotions, and cultural nuances continues to resonate with viewers, ensuring its enduring popularity.

snippet.title: कही नहीं देखी होगा सस्ते भुट्टे की ये रेसिपी 5 मिनट में बनए हफ्तों तक खाए | SWEET CORN CUTLET RECIPE
snippet.description:
Sweet Corn Cutlet Recipe #corncutlet – Banayein crispy aur chatpate Corn Cutlet ya Sweet Corn Kebab Tikki, jo perfect hai Evening Snacks Recipe ke liye! Is Corn Cutlet Recipe mein milega soft filling, crispy outer layer aur restaurant-style crunch. Chahe aap ise Corn Patties, Sweet Corn Vada, ya Corn Kabab Recipe ke naam se banayein – taste sab mein super yummy hai! Full video mein seekhiye how to make crispy corn kebab recipe with simple steps and kitchen ingredients. 

Preparation time - 20 minutes
Serving - 8

Ingredients : 
Raw Corn - 2 pcs
Carrot - 2 small pcs
Capsicum 
Ginger-Green Chili-Garlic Paste - 1 tbsp
Chopped Coriander
Coriander Powder - 1 tbsp
Turmeric - 2 pinch
Red Chilli Powder - 1 tsp
Cumin Powder - 1/2 tsp
Garam Masala - 1/2 tsp
Amchur Powder - 1 tsp
Salt as per Taste
Black Salt - 1/2 tsp
Gram Flour - 1/2 cup
Rice Flour - 3 tbsp

 corn cutlet recipe,corn cutlet,sweet corn cutlet recipe,corn cutlet recipe in tamil,corn cutlet recipe in marathi,how to make corn cutlet at home,how to make corn cutlet,sweet corn cutlet,cheese corn cutlet

snippet.title: RAIN + FOOD + TWIST = CRAZY FOOD CHALLENGE! ⛈️
snippet.description:
🌧️ Monsoon Food Madness with a Twist! 🌧️
Onkar, Mukti & Aditya are spinning the wheel of cravings! Each writes their top 3 rainy-season foods — but whoever lands on it, eats it alone. The others can only watch 😱
